# Copy this file to ".env" and set your own Twitch app Client ID.
# The .env file is never committed (see .gitignore).
#
# Create a PUBLIC Twitch app and paste its Client ID below.
# Full step-by-step: README.md → Setup.
#
# A Public app has NO client secret — the Client ID is public by design, so it's
# fine that each user brings their own here. Do NOT hardcode it in the source.

TWITCH_CLIENT_ID=
